  "blurb": "A contemporary three-plus-one-bedroom villa within one of Koh Samui’s most exclusive gated beachfront communities at Samrong Bay, Plai Laem — private beach access, stunning sea views and a private pool, moments from a secluded white-sand cove. Fully furnished, freehold Chanote title, with 24/7 security. ฿30,000,000.",
  "detail": "Located within one of Koh Samui’s most exclusive gated beachfront communities on the north-eastern tip of the island, this contemporary villa offers a rare blend of privacy, convenience and tropical luxury — just moments from a secluded white-sand beach. Peaceful surroundings, stunning sea views, and direct access to Samrong Bay, a serene cove known for its crystal-clear water and calm atmosphere.\n\nDesigned with the same premium layout concept as the estate’s neighbouring villas, the home features open-plan living, light-filled interiors and a seamless flow to the outdoor terrace and private pool. A modern Western kitchen, a generous living area, and a flexible multipurpose room — ideal as an office, gym or fourth bedroom — make it suited equally to full-time living or a high-yield holiday rental.\n\nThree en-suite bedrooms plus the flex room and four bathrooms are wrapped in floor-to-ceiling glass, with sea-view aspects throughout and a terrace made for sunrise. The property is held freehold on a Chanote title, fully furnished and move-in ready, within a gated estate with 24/7 onsite security and private road access.\n\nSamrong Bay is one of the few communities on the island to offer both tranquillity and immediate access to key amenities — around five minutes to Choeng Mon, ten to Bang Rak and Fisherman’s Village, and fifteen to Chaweng: the best of Samui living, an exclusive beachfront lifestyle paired with unmatched convenience.",
